<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>什么是二级缓存</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">二级缓存是用来解决一级缓存不能跨会话共享的问题的，范围是</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">namespace </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">级别的，可以被多个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">共享（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">只要是同一个接口里面的相同方法，都可以共享</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），生命周期和应用同步。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">二级缓存是一个作用范围更广的缓存，它在</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的外层，能被多个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">共享。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">因此<strong>工作在一级缓存之前</strong>，也就是只有取不到二级缓存的情况下才到一个会话中去取一级缓存</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">如果你的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">使用了二级缓存，并且你的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Mapper</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">select</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语句也配置使用了二级缓存</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">查询数据的顺序是：二级缓存——</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&gt;</span> <span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一级缓存——</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&gt; </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">数据库。</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实际上</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">MyBatis </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">用了一个装饰器的类（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">CachingExecutor</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）来维护。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">如果启用了二级缓存，</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">CachingExecutor </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对于查询请求，会判断二级缓存是否有缓存结果，如果有，就直接返回，如果没有，就交给真正的查询器</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Executor </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实现类</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><img
        src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:236px; width:483px"></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>开启二级缓存</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">配置</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> mybatis.configuration</span></span></li>
</ol>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;setting name="<span
                style="color:#f73131">cacheEnabled</span>" value="<span
                style="color:#f73131">true</span>"/&gt;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;/settings&gt;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">只要没有显式地设置</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">cacheEnabled=false</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，都会用</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">CachingExecutor </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">装饰基本的执行器。</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="2"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Mapper.xml </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">中配置</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;cache/&gt;</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签</span></span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>语法</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#000088">&lt;cache/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这个简单语句的效果如下</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">:</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">映射语句文件中的所有</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> select </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语句的结果将会被缓存。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">映射语句文件中的所有</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> insert</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">update </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> delete </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语句会刷新缓存。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">缓存会使用最近最少使用算法（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">LRU, Least Recently
                Used</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）算法来清除不需要的缓存。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">缓存不会定时进行刷新（也就是说，没有刷新间隔）。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">缓存会保存列表或对象（无论查询方法返回哪种）的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 1024 </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">个引用。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">缓存会被视为读</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">/</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">写缓存，这意味着获取到的对象并不是共享的，可以安全地被调用者修改，而不干扰其他调用者或线程所做的潜在修改。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span

                </ul>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                                style="color:black">最近最少使用：移除最长时间不被使用的对象。</span></span></span></p>

                </ul>

                                style="color:black">软引用：基于垃圾回收器状态和软引用规则移除对象。</span></span></span></p>
                <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
                    <li><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">WEAK</span></span></li>
                </ul>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                                style="color:black">弱引用：更积极地基于垃圾收集器状态和弱引用规则移除对象</span></span></span></p>
            </td>

                            因此这些对象不能被修改。这就提供了可观的性能提升。而可读写的缓存会（通过序列化）返回缓存对象的拷贝。 速度上会慢一些，但是更安全</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#70ad47"><strong>示例</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#000088">&lt;cache</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;
            <span style="color:#660066">eviction</span><span style="color:#666600">=</span><span
                style="color:#008800">"FIFO"</span><br>&nbsp; <span style="color:#660066">flushInterval</span><span
                style="color:#666600">=</span><span style="color:#008800">"60000"</span><br>&nbsp; <span
                style="color:#660066">size</span><span style="color:#666600">=</span><span
                style="color:#008800">"512"</span><br>&nbsp; <span style="color:#660066">readOnly</span><span
                style="color:#666600">=</span><span style="color:#008800">"true"</span><span
                style="color:#000088">/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#000088">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:black"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这个更高级的配置创建了一个</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> FIFO </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">缓存，每隔</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 60 </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">秒刷新，最多可以存储结果对象或列表的</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 512 </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">个引用，而且返回的对象被认为是只读的，因此对它们进行修改可能会在不同线程中的调用者产生冲突</span></span></span>
</p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><strong>注</strong></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">二级缓存是事务性的。当</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> SqlSession </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">完成并提交时，或是完成并回滚，但没有执行</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> flushCache=true
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> insert/delete/update </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语句时，缓存会获得更新。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">同一命名空间中的所有语句和缓存将通过命名空间绑定在一起。
                每条语句可以自定义与缓存交互的方式，或将它们完全排除于缓存之外，这可以通过在每条语句上使用两个简单属性来达成。 </span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#333333">默认情况下，语句会这样来配置：</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#70ad47"><strong>示例</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#000088">&lt;select</span><span style="color:black"> ... </span><span
                style="color:#660066">flushCache</span><span style="color:#666600">=</span><span
                style="color:#008800">"false" </span><span style="color:#660066">useCache</span><span
                style="color:#666600">=</span><span style="color:#008800">"true"</span><span
                style="color:#000088">/&gt;</span><br><span style="color:#000088">&lt;insert</span><span
                style="color:black"> ... </span><span style="color:#660066">flushCache</span><span
                style="color:#666600">=</span><span style="color:#008800">"true"</span><span
                style="color:#000088">/&gt;</span><br><span style="color:#000088">&lt;update</span><span
                style="color:black"> ... </span><span style="color:#660066">flushCache</span><span
                style="color:#666600">=</span><span style="color:#008800">"true"</span><span
                style="color:#000088">/&gt;</span><br><span style="color:#000088">&lt;delete</span><span
                style="color:black"> ... </span><span style="color:#660066">flushCache</span><span
                style="color:#666600">=</span><span style="color:#008800">"true"</span><span
                style="color:#000088">/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#000088">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">但如果你想改变默认的行为，只需要设置</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> flushCache </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> useCache </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#333333"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">比如，某些情况下你可能希望特定</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> select </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语句的结果排除于缓存之外，或希望一条</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> select </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语句清空缓存。</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">引用其他缓存</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#333333">cache-ref</span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#333333"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对某一命名空间的语句，只会使用该命名空间的缓存进行缓存或刷新。
                但你可能会想要在多个命名空间中共享相同的缓存配置和实例。要实现这种需求，你可以使用</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                cache-ref </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素来引用另一个缓存。</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#70ad47"><strong>示例</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#000088">&lt;cache-ref </span><span style="color:#660066">namespace</span><span
                style="color:#666600">=</span><span
                style="color:#008800">"com.someone.application.data.SomeMapper"</span><span
                style="color:#000088">/&gt;</span></span></span></p>
